AI XP Farming

An AI doesn’t inherently gain wisdom from existing.

It gains “XP” from:

* User interactions
* Feedback loops
* Evaluation results
* Success/failure signals
* Novel situations
* Contradictions

The raw data matters less than the difference between prediction and reality.

That difference is the XP source.

